\[p \coloneqq\Pr(X\geq r)=\Phi\bigg{(}\frac{-r}{\sigma}\bigg{)},\] \[q \coloneqq\Pr(X+\epsilon\geq 0\mid X\geq r)=\frac{1}{p}\int_{r}^{ \infty}\int_{-x}^{\infty}\frac{\exp\left(\frac{-x^{2}}{2\sigma^{2}}\right)}{ \sqrt{2\pi\sigma^{2}}}\frac{\exp\left(\frac{-y^{2}}{2}\right)}{\sqrt{2\pi}} \mathrm{d}y\mathrm{d}x=\frac{M(r,\sigma^{2})}{p},\]

